.TH xentop 1M "3 Mar 2008" "SunOS 5.11" "System Administration Commands"
.SH NAME
xentop \- display real-time information about an xVM system and domains
.SH SYNOPSIS
.LP
.nf
\fBxentop\fR [\fB-h\fR] [\fB-V\fR] [\fB-d\fR=\fIseconds\fR] [\fB-n\fR] [\fB-r\fR]  [\fB-v\fR] [\fB-b\fR] [\fB-i\fR=\fIiterations\fR]
.fi

.SH DESCRIPTION
.sp
.LP
The \fBxentop\fR command displays information about the Solaris xVM system
and domains in a continually-updating way. It is analogous to the BSD UNIX
\fBtop\fR command.
.SH OPTIONS
.sp
.LP
The following options are supported:
.sp
.ne 2
.mk
.na
\fB\fB-b\fR, \fB--batch\fR\fR
.ad
.sp .6
.RS 4n
Output data to stdout in batch mode.
.RE

.sp
.ne 2
.mk
.na
\fB\fB-d\fR, \fB--delay\fR=\fIseconds\fR\fR
.ad
.sp .6
.RS 4n
Set seconds between updates. The default is 3 seconds.
.RE

.sp
.ne 2
.mk
.na
\fB\fB-h\fR, \fB--help\fR\fR
.ad
.sp .6
.RS 4n
Display help and exit.
.RE

.sp
.ne 2
.mk
.na
\fB\fB-i\fR, \fB--iterations\fR=\fIiterations\fR\fR
.ad
.sp .6
.RS 4n
Maximum number of iterations \fBxentop\fR should display before
terminating.
.RE

.sp
.ne 2
.mk
.na
\fB\fB-n\fR, \fB--networks\fR\fR
.ad
.sp .6
.RS 4n
Display network information.
.RE

.sp
.ne 2
.mk
.na
\fB\fB-r\fR, \fB--repeat-header\fR\fR
.ad
.sp .6
.RS 4n
Repeat table header before each domain.
.RE

.sp
.ne 2
.mk
.na
\fB\fB-v\fR, \fB--vcpus\fR\fR
.ad
.sp .6
.RS 4n
Display VCPU data.
.RE

.sp
.ne 2
.mk
.na
\fB\fB-V\fR, \fB--version\fR\fR
.ad
.sp .6
.RS 4n
Display version information and exit.
.RE

.sp
.ne 2
.mk
.na
\fB\fB-x\fR, \fB--vbds\fR\fR
.ad
.sp .6
.RS 4n
Display virtual block device data.
.RE

.SH INTERACTIVE COMMANDS
.sp
.LP
The \fBxentop\fR command supports a set of interactive commands. These are
one-letter (case-insensitive) commands that you enter while \fBxentop\fR
output is displayed. They are as follows:
.sp
.ne 2
.mk
.na
\fB\fBd\fR\fR
.ad
.sp .6
.RS 4n
Set delay between updates.
.RE

.sp
.ne 2
.mk
.na
\fB\fBn\fR\fR
.ad
.sp .6
.RS 4n
Toggle display of network information.
.RE

.sp
.ne 2
.mk
.na
\fB\fBq\fR, \fBEsc\fR\fR
.ad
.sp .6
.RS 4n
Quit.
.RE

.sp
.ne 2
.mk
.na
\fB\fBr\fR\fR
.ad
.sp .6
.RS 4n
Toggle table header before each domain.
.RE

.sp
.ne 2
.mk
.na
\fB\fBs\fR\fR
.ad
.sp .6
.RS 4n
Cycle sort order.
.RE

.sp
.ne 2
.mk
.na
\fB\fBv\fR\fR
.ad
.sp .6
.RS 4n
Toggle display of VCPU information.
.RE

.sp
.ne 2
.mk
.na
\fB(arrow keys)\fR
.ad
.sp .6
.RS 4n
Scroll domain display.
.RE

